Contains scripts and input files for
"Functional domain interactions in a nonribosomal peptide synthetase monitored
by FRET"
Tom Morrell 8/2016

-minimize.inp - Set up structure and do energy minimization
-sampling.inp - Run with SPSMF.py using command python SPSMF.py sampling grsa_min 16 152
-correct_dcd.inp - Correct number of accepted conformations in dcd file
-dye_dist.inp - Calculate dye positions
-det_dye.py - Process dye positions using command python det_dye.py input
-preplinker.inp - Set up linker
-ld.inp - Run dynamics for linker
-extract_pdb.py - Pull out individual pdb files from trajectory
-align_egfp.inp - Add egfp to model
-sampling_egfp - sample egfp conformations - you'll need to make a nolinker
file which has structure without linker
-correct_dcd_egfp.inp - Correct number of accepted egfp positions
-correl_egfp.inp - Calculate egfp positions
-det_egfp.py - Process egfp positions using command python det_egfp.py
input_gfp
